對波都幾大下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大到傷盡少女心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"651a302095f3236226e115a4d1768e39b728750d","tid":167231,"uid":6238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T08:44:19.000Z","msg":"試過Arimidex 未"},{"pid":"f563c5e83f262fa8d8609ee72002ff8840e419f9","tid":167231,"uid":93630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T08:44:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可以揸自己</blockquote><br />\n光明正大咁戴波罩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceeca7d251f56cc90ef293810e8e4cacf9b9310e","tid":167231,"uid":23467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T09:13:32.000Z","msg":"除非係集中乳頭範圍尖凸<br />\n先似男性女乳症<br />\n<br />\n眼見啲朋友<br />\n好多時都係脂肪積聚肥仔波<br />\n唔係話超級大肥仔先有<br />\n每個人積聚脂肪位置、比例都唔同<br />\n<br />\n所以<br />\n試下減完體脂都仲有先考慮搵醫生吧<br />\n路過9up<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ed3a3ad8825e889408ecd0a494bc81a8c6eb0d1","tid":167231,"uid":87550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T14:07:24.000Z","msg":"我微胖啦，但之前淨係做重訓忽略左減脂，所以變左胸肌上再有脂肪，所以變得更大    掛"},{"pid":"8825b6170885f8373d91efc06c4dff7e0378f0c7","tid":167231,"uid":10249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T14:16:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L0AQKoV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL0AQKoV.jpg&h=5db48e33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n肥仔波"}]}